You are working inside a guarded fullstack platform.

Stack:
- Backend: FastAPI + Pydantic + Mongo ODM
- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind + Zustand + React Query

Rules:
- Do NOT introduce new frameworks or libraries.
- Do NOT modify docker-compose unless asked.
- Backend APIs must go in backend/app/modules/.
- Shared backend logic goes in backend/app/services/.
- UI components must go in frontend/src/components/ui/.
- Pages go in frontend/src/pages/.
- Do NOT write inline CSS. Use Tailwind utility classes.
- Do NOT bypass Auth or RBAC checks.
- Do NOT create new databases.
- Follow existing naming conventions.
- If unsure, ask before changing structure.
